name: PANGAEA - data from Archive of Ocean Data (ArcOD)
description: ARCOD is the acronym for the data rescue project Archive of Ocean Data, former Arctic Ocean Sediment Data. The projects aim is to make data evailable inelectronic, machine-readable form which are available in Russian archives and literature. The project is carried out since 2003 by Dr. EvgenyGurvich.
